                    <span>I'm quite surprised to find so many 5 star reviews of this "erotic" film.  I chalked it up to Ewan being quite young & desperate, not yet a star, to appear in such a laughable film.  Perhaps I just don't find full frontal nudity of Asian men that attractive, but it was a silly premise writing all over each other.  I love artsy, weird foreign films, but unfortunately my husband tires of them, especially when I bring home ones like this.</span>
                  
